  "title": "Famous Noodle Shop Restaurant Manager )",
  "description": "<p>Take care of outlet operations</p><p>Ensure the satisfaction of customers and clients.<br /><br />Recommendation of restaurant's dishes and wine pairing if required.</p><p>Rostering of employees.</p><p>Ensure inventory is sufficient for the operation of the outlet, and order when stocks are low.</p><p>Ensure outlet is well kept and regularly cleaned and free from pests.</p><p>Willing and able to fill in roles where employees are absent on medical or leave or short handed.</p><p>(eg Mop clean floors / Wash dishes / Collect dishes and clear/clean tables / cashiering).</p><p>Willing to work split shifts (eg 10am to 2pm and 6pm to 10pm).</p><p>6 days per week, rest day will be weekdays.</p><p>Willing to work weekends and holidays.<br /><br />Valid Class 3 license.</p>",
